<% include header %>

<body>
    <h1>Actor Contact and Basic Info</h1>
    <p id="con">Please fill out the starred questions and submit this form BEFORE you come to the costume shop to have
        your measurements taken.
        You MUST have a copy of this form on file before the shop staff will measure you.
        Please have your schedule of availability ready when you arrive for measurements.</p>

    <div class="container">

        <form id="contactForm">
            <label for="namelf">Name(Last)</label>
            <input type="text" name="namef" id="namel" value="" required><br>

            <label for="namelf">Name(First)</label>
            <input type="text" name="namef" id="namef" value="" required><br>

            <label for="charName">Character Name: </label>
            <input type="text" name="charName" id="charName" value="" required><br>

            <label for="phone">Phone number:</label>
            <input type="text" name="phone" id="phone" value="" required><br>

            <label for="age">Age:</label>
            <input type="text" name="age" id="age" value="" required><br>

            <label for="addr1">Address Line 1:</label>
            <input type="text" name="age" id="addr1" value="" required><br>

            <label for="addr2">Address Line 2:</label>
            <input type="text" name="age" id="addr2" value="" required><br>

            <label for="country">Country:</label>
            <input type="text" name="age" id="country" value="" required><br>

            <label for="textyou">May we text you? </label><br>
            <input type="radio" name="textu" id="textu_y" value=""> Yes<br>
            <input type="radio" name="textu" id="textu_n" value=""> No<br><br>

            <label for="email">University email address</label>
            <input type="email" name="email" id="email" value="" required><br>

            <p>"I understand that I must check my Northwest student email DAILY as requests for fitting appointments
                will be sent to that email. I will respond to a fitting request as soon as possible. I understand that
                failing to check my university email does not excuse me from missing a fitting appointment. Missed
                appointments will be rescheduled at the discretion of the Costume Shop." *</p>
            <input type="checkbox" name="declare" id="declare" value="yes"> Yes, I understand<br><br>

            <label for="Hand">Dominant Hand</label><br>
            <input type="radio" name="hand" value="" id="right_hand"> Right<br>
            <input type="radio" name="hand" value="" id="left_hand"> Left <br>

            <label for="weight">Estimated weight</label>
            <p>Why? Your weight helps determine the right size for certain garments, such as dancewear and tights.</p>
            <input type="text" name="weight" id="weight" value="" required><br><br>

            <label for="height">Estimated height</label>
            <p>Why? Your height helps determine the length for certain garments.</p>
            <input type="text" name="height" id="height" value="" required><br><br>

            <label for="eyeware">Corrective Eyeware</label>
            <p>Please select all that apply</p>
            <input type="checkbox" class="eyeware" name="none" id="none" value="none"> None<br>
            <input type="checkbox" class="eyeware" name="glasses" id="glasses" value="glasses"> Glasses<br>
            <input type="checkbox" class="eyeware" name="contacts" id="contacts" value="contacts"> Contacts<br>
            <input type="checkbox" class="eyeware" name="fine" id="fine" value="fine"> I wear glasses but can perform
            without them<br>

            <label for="haircolor">Hair color and length</label>
            <input type="text" name="haircolor" id="haircolor" value=""><br><br>

            <label for="haircolor">Eye color</label>
            <input type="text" name="eyecolor" id="eyecolor" value="" required><br><br>

            <label for="facialHair">Facial Hair: color, length, and growth time</label>
            <p>If you cannot grow facial hair, please answer "none"</p>
            <input type="text" name="facialHair" id="facialHair" value="" required><br>

            <p>I understand that I may not permanently change the color, length, or style of my hair between casting
                and performance without the express permission of both the Costume Designer and Artistic Director.</p>
            <input type="checkbox" name="declare" id="declare_change" value="yes" required> Yes, I understand<br><br>

            <label for="piercings"> Do you have pierced ears?</label><br>
            <input type="radio" name="ear" id="pierce_yes" value="yes"> Yes <br>
            <input type="radio" name="ear" id="pierce_no" value="no"> No <br>

            <label for="otherPiercings">Do you have any other piercings? How many and where?</label>
            <input type="text" name="piercing" id="piercing" value="" required><br>

            <label for="tatto">Do you have any tattoos?</label>
            <p>If yes, please briefly describe size, location, and color</p>
            <input type="text" name="tatto" id="tatto" value="" required><br>

            <p>"I understand that if I have tattos I must provide my own tattoo cover makeup if asked. I understand
                that if I have piercings I may be asked to remove them or provide my own clear spacer during
                performances. I understand that I am not allowed to permanently alter my body with additional tattoos,
                piercings, etc. between casting and performance."</p>
            <input type="checkbox" name="declare" name="tatto_yes" value="yes" required> Yes, I understand<br>

            <label>_______________________________COMMENTS ABOUT THE BODY (OR COSTUME) OF ANY PERFORMER (YOURSELF
                INCLUDED) WILL NOT BE TOLERATED FROM ANY PERFORMER OR MEMBER OF THE PRODUCTION STAFF.</label>
            <p>From "Costume Related Questions for New Theatre Professionals" in the body of the Measurement Request
                email from Stage Management.</p>
            <input type="text" name="conclude" id="conclude" value="" required><br>

            <h2>Commercial Sizes</h2>

            <label for="shoes">Shoes</label>
            <input type="text" name="shoes" id="shoes" value="" required><br><br>

            <label for="dshoes">Dance Shoes: Size and Type</label>
            <input type="text" name="dshoes" id="dshoes" value="" required><br><br>

            <label for="shirt">Shirt</label>
            <p>If you know your men's dress shirt size (i.e. 15/34-35) please indicate in "other"</p>
            <input class="shirtsize" type="checkbox" id="xs" value="xs"> XS <br>
            <input class="shirtsize" type="checkbox" id="s" value="s"> S <br>
            <input class="shirtsize" type="checkbox" id="m" value="m"> M <br>
            <input class="shirtsize" type="checkbox" id="l" value="l"> L <br>
            <input class="shirtsize" type="checkbox" id="xl" value="xl"> XL <br>
            <input class="shirtsize" type="checkbox" id="xxl" value="xxl"> XXL <br>
            <input class="shirtsize" type="checkbox" id="xxxl" value="xxxl"> XXXL <br>
            <input class="shirtsize" type="checkbox" id="xxxxl" value="xxxxl"> XXXXL <br>
            <input class="shirtsize" type="checkbox" id="other" value="other"> Other <br>

            <label for="pants">Pants</label>
            <p>e.g. 8 (women) or 34x32 (waist by inseam for men)</p>
            <input type="text" name="pants" id="pants" value="" required><br>

            <label for="bsize">Bra Size</label><br>
            <input type="text" name="bsize" id="bsize" value=""><br>

            <label for="ring">Ring</label><br>
            <input type="text" name="ring" id="ring" value="" required><br>

            <label>Are you allergic to any of the following?</label><br>
            <input class="allergy" type="checkbox" name="fabric" id="fabric" value="fabric"> Fabric/Fibre <br>
            <input class="allergy" type="checkbox" name="detergent" id="detergent" value="detergent"> Detergent <br>
            <input class="allergy" type="checkbox" name="environmental" id="environmental" value="environmental">
            Environmental <br>
            <input class="allergy" type="checkbox" name="fragrance" id="fragrance" value="fragrance"> Fragrance <br>
            <input class="allergy" type="checkbox" name="metal" id="metal" value="metal"> Metal <br>
            <input class="allergy" type="checkbox" name="noall" id="noall" value="noall"> No Allergies <br>
            <input class="allergy" type="checkbox" name="other" id="other" value="other"> Other <br>

            <label>If you have allergies, please give specific details here.</label>
            <input type="text" name="anyall" id="anyall" value="" required><br><br>

            <label>Medications:</label>
            <input type="text" name="anyall" id="medi" value="" required><br><br>

            <label>Suggestions:</label>
            <input type="text" name="anyall" id="sugg" value="" required><br><br>
            <p>Upload an image (Please save the image with your first and last name)</p>
            <!-- <input type="file" id="myFile" multiple size="50" onchange="myFunction()"> -->

            <style>
                
progress {
  border: none;
  width: 100%;
  height: 30px;
  background: white;
  text-align: center
  
}

